Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and Sanji who had parted ways\Nfinally reunited at the rendezvous.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna crash Big Mom's \Ntea party and the wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and save Sanji's family!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Sanji'll be back with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the meeting on the assassination of\Nthe Emperor of the Sea - Big Mom, has begun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like it's the most \Nimportant treasure for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we break that picture in half,\Nwhat do you think will happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to take that role, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Luffy Engages in a Secret Maneuver!\NThe Wedding Full of Conspiracies Starts Soon!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how dangerous it is\Nto break Mama's precious portrait of Mother Carmel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to think twice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just came up with an awesome way\Nto show up at the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A way to show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What is it?\NSounds like fun! I wanna hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. If I tell you now,\Nit'll ruin the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}--What was I worried for?\N--What was I worried for?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.\NThen, I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, do you know when to break the picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Sanji kisses Pudding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, I won't do it! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You won't kiss her?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear what Brook said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wedding kiss\Nwill draw everyone's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.15,0:04:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pudding-{\i1}san{\i0} will shoot Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll dodge the shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the gunshot is the cue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! That's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's go over the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Pudding shoots the gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat breaks the picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom will shriek.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll put the Invisible \NSymphonia System on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say "earplugs."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it's all downhill from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While the people are in a panic,\Nyou guys will rescue Germa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with the KX Launcher\Nand the deadly poison gas shell,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll assassinate Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish everything in 10 seconds tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, the longer we stay there,\Nthe more likely are we to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a race against time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph!\NThat's the first rule of assassinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all depends on Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After he breaks the picture,\Nthere'll be three seconds before Mama starts crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not he can stop the Ministers\Nwho'll come attacking is the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do we escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as we kill Big Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.55,0:06:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this dumbass will come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dumbass"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's such a piece of crap.\N--Is this jerk part of the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, since I can fly,\NI'll plunge into the site with a mirror to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't count me in! Mama will kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys did a great job\Nbringing Brulee here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't have hoped for a more useful power\Nto help us escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your compliment doesn't \Nmake me happy, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you finish,\Ndive into Caesar's mirror quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom will still be shrieking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, we can just run away\Nin the mirror dimension in comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of a mirror that is big enough\Nfor you to come out on your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the dresser!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mirror will provide you the quickest way\Nto escape from the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Through the Mirroworld,\Nwe can get to the Sunny in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think it's gonna work well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pedro is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make even one small mistake,\Nyou'll face death...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how dangerous it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}These bastards...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once each of us gets to our own ships,\Nour alliance is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:08:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should just get out of this territory\Nas fast as we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're set.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The party starts at 10, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two and a half hours to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go back to my room\Nsince I'm the groom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to go back too.\NLet's get ready for fake security duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bege. Could you do me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I show up in a funny way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to be funny!\NYou're gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well...\N--Our Bobbin the Disposer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who killed him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We haven't found the killer yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're investigating!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:08:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did he get shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably, late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat? No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Opera said he burned Straw Hat\Nand Cat Burglar to death after torturing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about that.\NI can't trust him until I see their dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone saw Sanji-{\i1}sama{\i0} heading to\Nthe outskirts of the city late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat and Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If either of them killed Bobbin...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wedding is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:43.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,IN FRONT OF SANJI'S ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.22,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any visitors?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we saw him sleeping in his bed last night,\Nno one entered or left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! I am sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.24,0:10:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji! You there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}?! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O... O... Oh no-{\i1}nasu.{\i0}..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}'s disappearance,\Nif they find out that I was sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mama will kill me-{\i1}nasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! Aren't you there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do-{\i1}nasu{\i0}?! What should I do-{\i1}nasu{\i0}?!\NWhat should I do-{\i1}nasu{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying...\NWhat do you want from me this early?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you in the room this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone who can prove\Nthat you were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ordered a soldier to watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Eggplant Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes-{\i1}nasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was Sanji here the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes-{\i1}nasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes-{\i1}nasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta get ready for the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat is still alive and plotting something\Nsecretly with you, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:12:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a prince of Germa Kingdom\Nwho will marry Big Mom's daughter today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if a low-class pirate plots something\Nor dies a dog's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my preparation runs late because of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mom'll get mad, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You surprised me-{\i1}nasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do-{\i1}nasu{\i0}?! \NWhat should I do-{\i1}nasu{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do-{\i1}nasu{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Be quiet and do as I say.\NIt's for your own good too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nwhere have you been until now-{\i1}nasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.\NI went out to deliver Pudding-{\i1}chan {\i0}food{\i1}.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right-{\i1}nasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask what happened after that.\NIt's not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay-{\i1}nasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:42.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,CHEESE TOWN, MILK ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:42.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is a holiday because of the Tea Party!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's celebrate with Supreme cheese and beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Pudding-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s old enough to marry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The groom is Germa 66's third son.\NWe'll have a strong ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:57.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PEANUT TOWN, NUTS ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The family of the Du Feld \NConglomerate has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:14:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch of celebrities will attend as guests!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little too early!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:07.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,CHOCOLAT TOWN, CACAO ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.69,0:14:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's Sanji-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The escort soldiers couldn't \Neven enter the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, we can't attend either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.\NNo one needs a guard for a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it should be a peaceful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:28.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,WHOLE CAKE CHATEAU
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone from the Vinsmoke Family,\Ngood morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:36.64,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up and change!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.79,0:14:39.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SIXTH FLOOR - A GUEST ROOM IN THE BAUM CAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:39.94,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Reiju? \NShe's not in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:43.65,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah,\NI haven't seen her since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.65,0:14:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Reiju-{\i1}sama {\i0}finished with her preparations\Nin another room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is still an hour before the Tea Party\Nso take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:00.96,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:03.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NINTH FLOOR - BIG MOM'S BEDROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the Ministers!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:11.89,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not moving! It's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:15.29,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My lovely skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad but, Mama...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, you have the Tea Party\Nthat you've been waiting for...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The wedding cake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Morgans and all the other VIPs\Nhave already arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:54.78,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,EASTERN INLET, WHOLE CAKE ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do this to me!\NUntie me, Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:09.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ALADDIN\NTHE FIRST MATE OF THE SUN PIRATES
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:06.32,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave some water and food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:09.40,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry but I'm sure \Nsomeone'll find you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:14.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you guys going?! Grr!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'll leave this country.\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you guys were\Ncarrying out your stuff all night long...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the Big Mom Pirates' affiliate\Nand you're leaving the country...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you're betraying Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she know about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let her know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll kill those who leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's who she is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei expresses his gratitude to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He does?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're very lucky to hear Pekoms' story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:17:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Bege can pull off his plan\Nto kill Big Mom that easily
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't believe Mama is plotting\Nan assassination of Germa too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Luffy and his clan find out about it,\Nthey'll push themselves to save Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be in danger and I can't just sit back!\NI've got to help them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means I will raise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a full-fledged rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,CHARLOTTE PRALINE\N21TH DAUGHTER OF CHARLOTTE, MARRIED TO ALADDIN
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:30.02,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I will betray Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To fufill my duty to her,\NI once told her directly that I was leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I took it back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because of the numbers\Nwritten on the roulette.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those numbers represent the number of my friends\Nwho would be victimized along with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I need you all\Nto get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The price that Big Mom wanted me to pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:18:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was an unreasonable sanction\Nthat was more than taking my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the day of the Tea Party, \Nthe Hors-d'oeuvre Ships,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,interceptors from each island, \Nwill escort the guests
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and security will be lax.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.11,0:18:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if something happens at the Tea Party,\Nit'll draw everyone's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's your chance to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. We'll take the chance\Nand break out of Totto Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still a deadly venture.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm prepared for that.\NThat's not a problem - but Jimbei,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we just want to help you to become free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save Straw Hat,\Nyou'll even sacrifice yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say I join the Straw Hats one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:19:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fight for the captain Straw Hat Luffy\Nat the price of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aladdin, it's just a matter of...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...doing it now or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.67,0:19:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Do as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do your best to save your own life too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll set sail for the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Big Mom finds out that we left her crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she may turn her rage on the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about the Ryugu Kingdom too,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll save it at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it!\NWe've known each other for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll live to see each other again,\NJimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Jimbei feel grateful to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, did he tell Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get ready to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where've you been, Reiju?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you guys were partying until late.\NOf course, I asked them to change my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere with adult stuff, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.\NThe Tea Party will take place on the rooftop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we proud Germa 66 will have\NBig Mom's power on our side
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and rule the North Blue again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But most importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji hasn't run away, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both the groom and the bride are\Nfully prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you thinking, Sanji?\NWhy didn't you escape?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know what's going to happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be nice if we can make it out alive\Nbut this is the Emperor of the Sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll turn into a scene of carnage for sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.31,0:21:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pre-wedding jitters?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I kill that stupid-ass Sanji,\NI don't want his blood on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:22:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and in order to go back to being a good girl,\NI gotta erase everyone's memories.
